cu.explanation_en: Setting NR cell ID to 0 causes invalid cell identification, leading to cell configuration rejection and setup failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting local N address to null causes missing value error, preventing F1-U interface establishment and causing connection failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將本地 N 地址設定為 null 會導致缺失值錯誤，防止 F1-U 介面建立並造成連線失敗。
